lation-key> is disabled, it will not block stylesheets and style-tags.'=>'Le statut de ce <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Bloqueur de style</translation-key>. Si le <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Bloqueur de style</translation-key> est désactivé, il ne bloquera pas les feuilles de style et ni les balises de style.','Backend / Style Blockers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> configured.'=>'Aucun <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Bloqueur de style</translation-key> n\'est configuré.','Backend / Style Blockers / BreadcrumbStyle Blockers'=>'Bloqueurs de style','Backend / Style Blockers / HeadlineStyle Blockers'=>'Bloqueurs de style','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineHandles'=>'Handles','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Nom','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlinePhrases'=>'Expressions','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Statut','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> section?'=>'Quelle est la finalité de la section <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Bloqueurs de style</translation-key> ?','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Explication des symboles','Backend / Style Blockers / Tip / HeadlineLanguage independent'=>'Indépendant de la langue','Backend / Style Blockers / Tip / Text<translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> are configured independently for all languages.'=>'Les <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Bloqueurs de style</translation-key> sont configurés indépendamment pour toutes les langues.','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> section allows you to block <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> from <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> that, for example, embed <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> to load external fonts like <translation-key id="Google-Fonts">Google Fonts</translation-key>.'=>'La section <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Bloqueurs de style</translation-key> vous permet de bloquer les <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> des <translation-key id="Plugins">Plug-ins</translation-key> qui, par exemple, intègrent des <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> pour charger des polices externes comme <translation-key id="Google-Fonts">Google Fonts</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / TextOnce a <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is created, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> provides an unblock JavaScript that can be entered into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. The <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> becomes unblocked once a visitor consents to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Une fois qu\'un <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Bloqueur de style</translation-key> est créé, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> fournit un JavaScript de déblocage qui peut être saisi dans le champ <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Code opt in</translation-key> d\'un <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. La <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> est débloquée dès qu\'un visiteur donne son consentement au <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is enabled and actively prevents <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> execution if the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key