tre demande de licence n\'est pas valide.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> are not available until the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is created.'=>'Les <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> ne sont pas disponibles tant que le <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> n\'est pas créé.','Backend / Services / LabelAsynchronous Opt-out Code'=>'Code opt out asynchrone','Backend / Services / LabelBlock Cookies Before Consent'=>'Bloquer les cookies avant le consentement','Backend / Services / Label<translation-key id="Prioritize">Prioritize</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Prioritize">Prioriser</translation-key>','Backend / Services / HintThe <translation-key id="Opt-out-Code">Opt-out Code</translation-key> contains asynchronous JavaScript code that needs to executed to finish the Opt-out.'=>'Le <translation-key id="Opt-out-Code">Code opt out</translation-key> contient un code JavaScript asynchrone qui doit être exécuté pour terminer l\'opt out.','Backend / Services / HintIf enabled, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> tries to block cookies with the names from <translation-key id="Cookie-Name">Cookie Name</translation-key> until consent is given.'=>'Si cette option est activée, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> tente de bloquer les cookies portant les noms du <translation-key id="Cookie-Name">Nom cookie</translation-key> jusqu\'à ce qu\'un consentement soit donné.','Backend / License / Alert MessageLicense information refreshed successfully.'=>'Les informations relatives à la licence ont été actualisées avec succès.','Backend / Services / HintThe <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> is loaded in <strong><em>&lt;head&gt;</em></strong> and is executed before the page is fully loaded.'=>'Le <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Code opt in</translation-key> est chargé dans <strong><em>&lt;head&gt;</em></strong> et est exécuté avant que la page ne soit entièrement chargée.','Backend / License / Alert MessageLicense registered successfully.'=>'Licence enregistrée avec succès.','Backend / Service Location / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Location">Location</translation-key> configured.'=>'Aucune <translation-key id="Location">Adresse</translation-key> configurée.','Backend / License / Alert MessageLicense removed successfully.'=>'Licence retirée avec succès.','Backend / Service Location / ButtonAdd Location'=>'Ajouter une adresse','Backend / Service Location / LabelHostname'=>'Nom d\'hôte','Backend / License / BreadcrumbLicense'=>'Licence','Backend / Service Location / LabelPath'=>'Chemin d\'accès','Backend / License / Button TitleRefresh License Information'=>'Actualiser les informations relatives à la licence','Backend / Service Location / Headline<translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Locations">Adresses</translation-key>','Backend / License / Button TitleRemove License'=>'Retirer la licence','Backend / Service Location / Table HeadlineHostname'=>'Nom d\'hôte','Backend / License / LabelCloud Scans'=>'Analyses du cloud','Backend / Service Location / Table HeadlinePath'=>'Chemin d\'accès','Backend / License / LabelConfirm Refresh'=>'Confirmer l\'actualisation','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is a <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>?'=>'Qu\'est-ce qu\'un <translation-key id="Hostname">Nom d\'hôte</translation-key> ?','Backend / License / LabelLicense Key'=>'Clé de licence','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key> section?'=>'Quelle est la finalité de la section <translation-key id="Locations">Adresses</translation-key> ?','Backend / License / LabelLicense Name'=>'Nom de licence','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is the domain name of the website. For example, if the URL of the website is <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, the <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.'=>'Le <translation-key id="Hostname">Nom d\'hôte</translation-key> est le nom de domaine du site web. Par exemple, si l\'URL du site web est <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, le <translation-key id="Hostname">Nom d\'hôte</translation-key> est <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / License / LabelLicense Status'=>'Statut de licence','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / TextIt may happen that an embedded <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> on your website does not set a cookie, but a connection to a foreign domain is established. Therefore, it is advisable to record this domain here and thus name the service responsible for it, so that interested visitors can understand why this external connection occurs.'=>'Il peut arriver qu\'un <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> intégré à votre site web n\'établisse pas de cookie, mais qu\'une connexion à un domaine étranger soit établie. Il est donc conseillé d\'enregistrer ce domaine ici et de nommer ainsi le service qui en est responsable afin que les visiteurs intéressés puissent comprendre la raison de cette connexion externe.','Backend / License / LabelValid Until'=>'Valide jusqu\'au','Backend / Service Option / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Option">Option</translation-key> configured.'=>'Aucune <translation-key id="Option">Option</translation-key> n\'est configurée.','Backend / License / LabelMax Websites'=>'Nombre max. de sites web','Backend / Service Option / ButtonAdd Option'=>'Ajouter une option','Backend / License / LabelRefresh'=>'Actualiser','Backend / Service Option / LabelDescription'=>'Description','Backend / License / Headline<translation-key id="Remove-License">Remove License</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Remove-License">Retirer la licence</translation-key>','Backend / Service Option / Headline<translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key>','Backend / License / HeadlineYour License'=>'Votre licence','Backend / Service Option / Table HeadlineDescription'=>'Description','Backend / License / HeadlineYour License Information'=>'Vos informations de licence','Backend / Service Option / Table Headline<translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key>','Backend / License / HintEnter your License Key.'=>'Saisissez votre clé de licence.','Backend / Service Option / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> section?'=>'Quelle est la finalité de la section <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> ?','Backend / License / HintPlease confirm that you want to remove your license data from this website. After the license data is removed you are able to enter your new license key.'=>'Veuillez confirmer que vous souhaitez retirer les données de votre licence sur ce site web. Une fois les données de licence retirées, vous pourrez saisir votre nouvelle clé de licence.','Backend / Service Option / Things to know / TextWith <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> you can provide more information about the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. There are six <translation-key id="Types">Types</translation-key> to choose from and you can add as many <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> as you like.'=>'Les <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> vous permettent de fournir plus d\'informations sur le <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Vous avez le choix entre six <translation-key id="Types">Types</translation-key> et vous pouvez ajouter autant d\'<translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> que vous le souhaitez.','Backend / License / TextYour license has expired.'=>'Votre licence a expiré.','Backend / Service Option / Things to know / TextFor example, you could select the &quot;<translation-key id="Location-Processing">Location Processing</translation-key>&quot; <translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key> and add <strong>United States of America</strong> as description if the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> processes data in the United States.'=>'Par exemple, vous pouvez sélectionner le <translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key> &quot;<translation-key id="Location-Processing">Lieu du traitement</translation-key>&quot; et ajouter <strong>États-Unis d\'Amérique</strong> comme description si le <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> traite des données aux États-Unis.','Backend / License / TextYour license is valid.'=>'Votre licence est valide.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> configured.'=>'Aucun <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> configuré.','Backend / License / Things to know / HeadlineTransferring a license key to a new website'=>'Transfert d\'une clé de licence vers un nouveau site web','Backend / License / Things to know / TextYou can use the <translation-key id="Remove-License">Remove License</translation-key> option to remove the license from this website, or you can visit our <translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Customer Portal</translation-key> and remove the license from there.'=>'Vous pouvez utiliser l\'option <translation-key id="Remove-License">Retirer la licence</translation-key> pour retirer la licence de ce site web ou vous rendre sur notre <translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Portail client</translation-key> et retirer la licence à partir de là.','Backend / License / Things to know / Text<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span><translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Customer Portal</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>'=>'<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span><translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Portail client</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>','Backend / Local Scanner / TextAn error has occurred. Please check your browser\'s console for an error message. If the issue persists even after trying again and switching to <translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Scan Mode</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Manual">Manual</translation-key>, kindly reach out to our support team for assistance.'=>'Une erreur s\'est produite. Veuillez consulter la console de votre navigateur pour obtenir un message d\'erreur. Si le problème persiste même après avoir réessayé et basculé en <translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Mode analyse</translation-key> : <translation-key id="Manual">Manuel</translation-key>, veuillez contacter notre équipe de support pour obtenir de l\'aide.','Backend / Services / HeadlineReset Default Services'=>'Réinitialiser les services par défaut','Backend / Local Scanner / ButtonRun scan'=>'Lancer l\'analyse','Backend / Services / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings. Your custom <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> and the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key> are not reset.'=>'Veuillez confirmer que vous souhaitez réinitialiser tous les paramètres du <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Les paramètres par défaut seront rétablis. Vos <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> personnalisés et les <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> installés par l\'intermédiaire de la <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Bibliothèque</translation-key> ne sont pas réinitialisés.','Backend / Local Scanner / LabelPage to scan'=>'Page à analyser','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Local Scanner / Label<translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Scan Mode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Mode analyse</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Table HeadlinePosition'=>'Position','Backend / Local Scanner / Label<translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Expression de recherche</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Statut','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineScan Progress'=>'Progression de l\'analyse','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> section?'=>'Quelle est la finalité de la section <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> ?','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineScan Settings'=>'Paramètres analyse','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Explication des symboles','Backend / Local Scanner / HintThe string <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> is looking for. Separate multiple entries with a comma.'=>'La chaîne de caractères que <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> recherche. Séparer les entrées multiples par une virgule.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextIn the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> section you can document the use of services and their cookies for your visitors, as well as integrate JavaScripts, such as Google Analytics.'=>'Dans la section <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>, vous pouvez documenter l\'utilisation de services et de leurs cookies pour vos visiteurs, ainsi qu\'intégrer des JavaScripts, tels que Google Analytics.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextBecause <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> uses the opt-in process, JavaScripts are only executed after the visitor has given their consent to the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Étant donné que <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> utilise le processus d\'opt in, les consentements ne sont exécutés qu\'une fois que le visiteur a donné son accord au <translation-key id="Service-Group">Groupe de services</translation-key> ou au <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Scan-Modes">Scan Modes</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Scan-Modes">Modes analyse</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is active and displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'Le <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> est activé et affiché dans la <translation-key id="Dialog">Boîte de dialogue</translation-key>. Non disponible pour le <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> : <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Current-User">Current User</translation-key>:<br>The scan is performed as the currently logged in user. This may affect the results if the user has different rights than a guest user.'=>'<translation-key id="Current-User">Utilisateur actuel</translation-key> :<br>l\'analyse est effectuée par l\'utilisateur actuellement connecté. Cela peut affecter les résultats si l\'utilisateur a des droits différents de ceux d\'un utilisateur invité.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'Supprimer le <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Non disponible pour le <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> : <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineFor example: Some plugins do not embed tracking JavaScript for users with the role of an administrator.'=>'Par exemple : certains plug-ins n\'intègrent pas de JavaScript de suivi pour les utilisateurs ayant le rôle d\'administrateur.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Modifier le <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Guest">Guest</translation-key>:<br>The scan is performed as a guest user. This is the default setting.'=>'<translation-key id="Guest">Invité</translation-key> :<br>l\'analyse est effectuée en tant qu\'utilisateur invité. Il s\'agit du paramètre par défaut.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is inactive and not displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'Le <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> est inactivé et n\'est pas affiché dans la <translation-key id="Dialog">Boîte de dialogue</translation-key>. Non disponible pour le <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> : <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Manual">Manual</translation-key>:<br>When you use this mode, a signed URL is provided that you can use to run the scan by clicking on it. This is useful if the scan cannot be performed due to a server configuration or if your website is not accessible from the outside (<translation-key id="Local-Environment">Local Environment</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Staging-Environment">Staging Environment</translation-key>), for example.'=>'<translation-key id="Manual">Manuel</translation-key> :<br>lorsque vous utilisez ce mode, une URL signée est fournie que vous pouvez utiliser pour lancer l\'analyse en cliquant dessus. Ceci est utile si l\'analyse ne peut pas être effectuée en raison d\'une configuration de serveur ou si votre site web n\'est pas accessible depuis l\'extérieur (<translation-key id="Local-Environment">Environnement local</translation-key> ou <translation-key id="Staging-Environment">Environnement de simulation (staging)</translation-key>), par exemple.','Backend / Service Group / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Modifier : {{ name }}','Backend / Local Scanner / Alert MessageNo scan result available.'=>'Aucun résultat d\'analyse n\'est disponible.','Backend / Service Group / BreadcrumbService Groups'=>'Groupes de services','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Matched Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Handles avec correspondance</translation-key>','Backend / Service Group / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nouveau','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Matched Tags</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Balises avec correspondance</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelDescription'=>'Description','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Unmatched Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Handles sans correspondance</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Unmatched Tags</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Balises sans correspondance</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelName'=>'Nom','Backend / Local Scanner / HintSpecifies the name of the object that must be present for the script from the <strong>Tag</strong> column to be executed. Allowed characters include $, _, letters (both upper and lower case), and numbers. The first character must be $, _, or a letter, while subsequent characters can also include numbers.'=>'Script du nom de l\'objet qui doit être présent pour que le script de la colonne <strong>Balise</strong> soit exécuté. Les caractères autorisés sont $, _, les lettres (majuscules et minuscules) et les chiffres. Le premier caractère doit être $, _ ou une lettre, tandis que les caractères suivants peuvent également inclure des chiffres.','Backend / Service Groups / LabelPosition'=>'Position','Backend / Local Scanner / HintEnter a unique string found in the <strong>Tag</strong> to block the script. It should be unique enough that it is not found in other JavaScripts as well.'=>'Saisir une chaîne unique trouvée dans la <strong>Balise</strong> pour bloquer le script. Elle doit être suffisamment unique pour ne pas se retrouver dans d\'autres JavaScripts.','Backend / Service Groups / LabelPre-selected'=>'Pré-sélectionné','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineBlock'=>'Bloquer','Backend / Service Groups / Label<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Local Scanner / Table Headline<translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelStatus'=>'Statut','Backend / Local Scanner / Table Headline<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / HeadlineService Group Information'=>'Informations groupe de services','Backend / Local Scanner / Table Headline<translation-key id="Phrase">Phrase</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Phrase">Expression</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / HeadlineService Group Settings'=>'Paramètres groupes de services','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineTag'=>'Balise','Backend / Service Groups / HintEnter a description for this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. It is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Saisir une description pour ce <translation-key id="Service-Group">Groupe de services</translation-key>. Elle est affichée au visiteur dans la <translation-key id="Dialog">Boîte de dialogue</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineType'=>'Type','Backend / Service Groups / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> doit être défini. L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> doit être composé d\'au moins 3 caractères et ne peut contenir que : <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineURL'=>'URL','Backend / Service Groups / HintChoose a name for this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. It is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Choisir un nom pour ce <translation-key id="Service-Group">Groupe de services</translation-key>. Il est affiché au visiteur dans la <translation-key id="Dialog">Boîte de dialogue</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> are used to identify the JavaScript files that are loaded on your website. For example, your installed <translation-key id="Themes">Themes</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> use the WordPress function <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_script/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_script()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> to define the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>.'=>'Les <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> sont utilisés pour identifier les fichiers JavaScript qui sont chargés sur votre site web. Par exemple, vos <translation-key id="Themes">Thèmes</translation-key> et <translation-key id="Plugins">Plug-ins</translation-key> installés utilisent la fonction WordPress <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_script/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_script()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> pour définir les <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / HintDetermine the position where this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is displayed. Order follows natural numbers.'=>'Déterminer la position d\'affichage de ce <translation-key id="Service-Group">Groupe de services</translation-key>. L\'ordre suit celui des nombres naturels.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> are used to identify the <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> files that are loaded on your website. For example, your installed <translation-key id="Themes">Themes</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> use the WordPress function <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_style/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_style()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> to define the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>.'=>'Les <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> sont utilisés pour identifier les fichiers <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> qui sont chargés sur votre site web. Par exemple, vos <translation-key id="Themes">Thèmes</translation-key> et <translation-key id="Plugins">Plug-ins</translation-key> installés utilisent la fonction WordPress <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_style/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_style()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> pour définir les <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / HintIf enabled, this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is pre-selected in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. The visitor can de-select it.'=>'Si cette option est activée, ce <translation-key id="Service-Group">Groupe de services</translation-key> est présélectionné dans la <translation-key id="Dialog">Boîte de dialogue</translation-key>. Le visiteur peut le désélectionner.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Matched Handles</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> that matches your <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Handles avec correspondance</translation-key> :<br>il s\'agit des <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> qui correspondent à votre <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Expression de recherche</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / HintUse this <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to unblock JavaScript or content when user opted-in for this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>.'=>'Utilisez ce <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> pour débloquer JavaScript ou le contenu lorsque l\'utilisateur a opté pour ce <translation-key id="Service-Group">Groupe de services</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Unmatched Handles</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> that do not match a <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key> but were found during the scan and maybe relevant.'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Handles sans correspondance</translation-key> :<br>il s\'agit de <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> qui ne correspondent pas à une <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Expression de recherche</translation-key> mais qui ont été trouvés pendant l\'analyse et qui peuvent être pertinents.','Backend / Service Groups / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. If enabled it is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Statut de ce <translation-key id="Service-Group">Groupe de services</translation-key>. Si activé, il est affiché au visiteur dans la <translation-key id="Dialog">Boîte de dialogue</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> explained'=>'Explication des <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / Input Placeholder...block this...'=>'...bloquer ceci...','Backend / Local Scanner / Things to know / HeadlineInput fields explained'=>'Explication des champs de saisie','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> explained'=>'Explication du <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> explained'=>'Explication des <translation-key id="Tags">Balises</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> can be used to execute custom code once the visitor has given consent to a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> associated with this type of <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. This can be used, for example, to block a conversion pixel code.'=>'Le <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> peut être utilisé pour exécuter un code personnalisé une fois que le visiteur a donné son consentement à un <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> associé à ce type de <translation-key id="Service-Group">Groupe de services</translation-key>. Cela peut être utilisé, par exemple, pour bloquer un code de pixel de conversion.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> refer to <strong><em>&lt;script&gt;</em></strong> tags that lack an associated <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>, which can occur when JavaScript is embedded directly into your website\'s HTML code, bypassing the dedicated WordPress function typically used for this purpose'=>'Les <translation-key id="Tags">Balises</translation-key> se réfèrent aux balises <strong><em>&lt;script&gt;</em></strong> qui n\'ont pas de <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key> associé, ce qui peut se produire lorsque JavaScript est intégré directement dans le code HTML de votre site web, en contournant la fonction WordPress dédiée généralement utilisée à cette fin.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> refer to <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> tags and <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong> tags that lack an associated <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>, which can occur when <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> is embedded directly into your website\'s HTML code, bypassing the dedicated WordPress function typically used for this purpose'=>'Les <translation-key id="Tags">Balises</translation-key> se réfèrent à des balises <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> et à des balises <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong> qui n\'ont pas de <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key> associé, ce qui peut se produire lorsque <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> est incorporé directement dans le code HTML de votre site web, en contournant la fonction WordPress dédiée généralement utilisée à cette fin.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Matched Tags</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> that matches your <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Balises avec correspondance</translation-key> :<br>il s\'agit de <translation-key id="Tags">Balises</translation-key> qui correspondent à votre <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Expression de recherche</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Unmatched Tags</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> that do not match a <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key> but were found during the scan and maybe relevant.'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Balises sans correspondance</translation-key> :<br> il s\'agit de <translation-key id="Tags">Balises</translation-key> qui ne correspondent pas à une <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Expression de recherche</translation-key> mais qui ont été trouvées au cours de l\'analyse et qui peuvent être pertinentes.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Phrase">Phrase</translation-key>:<br>Enter a unique string found in the <strong>Tag</strong> to block the script. It should be unique enough that it is not found in other JavaScripts as well.'=>'<translation-key id="Phrase">Expression</translation-key> :<br>entrez une chaîne unique trouvée dans la <strong>Balise</strong> pour bloquer le script. Elle doit être suffisamment unique pour ne pas se retrouver dans d\'autres JavaScripts.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>:<br>This feature is optional and ensures that once the JavaScript is unblocked, it does not execute until the object specified in the <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key> column is present on the website. This capability facilitates the resolution of race condition issues.'=>'<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key> :<br>cette fonctionnalité est facultative et garantit qu\'une fois que le JavaScript est débloqué, il ne s\'exécute pas tant que l\'objet spécifié dans la colonne <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key> n\'est pas présent sur le site web. Cette fonctionnalité facilite la résolution des problèmes liés aux conditions de concurrence.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineSpecifies the name of the object that must be present for the script from the <strong>Tag</strong> column to be executed. Allowed characters include $, _, letters (both upper and lower case), and numbers. The first character must be $, _, or a letter, while subsequent characters can also include numbers.'=>'Script du nom de l\'objet qui doit être présent pour que le script de la colonne <strong>Balise</strong> soit exécuté. Les caractères autorisés sont $, _, les lettres (majuscules et minuscules) et les chiffres. Le premier caractère doit être $, _ ou une lettre, tandis que les caractères suivants peuvent également inclure des chiffres.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineExample:'=>'Exemple :','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineThe example initiates loading an external library and concurrently calls the <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> function. This could induce a race condition issue since, when <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> is invoked, the <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> library—responsible for providing this method—might not yet be fully loaded.'=>'L\'exemple lance le chargement d\'une bibliothèque externe et appelle simultanément la fonction <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> en même temps. Ceci pourrait induire un problème de condition de concurrence puisque, lorsque la fonction <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> est invoquée, la bibliothèque <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong>, chargée de fournir cette méthode, n\'est peut-être pas encore complètement chargée.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineTo mitigate this race condition, block both the script tag that loads the <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> library and the script tag that calls <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong>. For the script tag where <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> is called, enter <strong><em>calendarLibrary</em></strong> in the <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key> field.'=>'Pour atténuer cette condition de concurrence, bloquez à la fois la balise de script qui charge la bibliothèque <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> et la balise de script qui appelle la fonction <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong>. Pour la balise script où <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> est appelé, entrez <strong><em>calendarLibrary</em></strong> dans le champ <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineIf the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is now unblocked, the script-tag containing <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> will not execute until the <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> has completely loaded.'=>'Si le <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Bloqueur de script</translation-key> est maintenant débloqué, la balise de script contenant <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> ne s\'exécutera pas tant que le fichier <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> ne soit complètement chargé.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Phrase">Phrase</translation-key>:<br>Enter a unique string found in the <strong>Tag</strong> to block the <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key>. It should be unique enough that it is not found in other <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> tags or <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong> tags as well.'=>'<translation-key id="Phrase">Expression</translation-key> :<br>entrer une chaîne unique trouvée dans la <strong>Balise</strong> pour bloquer les <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key>. Elle doit être suffisamment unique pour ne pas être trouvée dans d\'autres balises <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> ou balises <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong>.','Backend / Local Scanner / ValidationThe phrase is not found in the JavaScript code on the left side.'=>'L\'expression ne se trouve pas dans le code JavaScript sur le côté gauche.','Backend / Local Scanner / ValidationThe phrase is not unique and overlaps with a phrase for another JavaScript.'=>'L\'expression n\'est pas unique et fait double emploi avec une expression pour un autre JavaScript.','Backend / Log / Alert MessageThe <translation-key id="Log">Log</translation-key> could not be found.'=>'Les <translation-key id="Log">Journaux</translation-key> n\'ont pas pu être trouvés.','Backend 