 id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> de blocage pour vous assurer qu\'il ne s\'exécute qu\'après avoir reçu le consentement. Cette fonctionnalité s\'avère utile dans des scénarios tels que la nécessité de déclencher un pixel de conversion exclusivement sur cette page.','Backend / Providers / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Modifier : {{ name }}','Backend / Providers / BreadcrumbProviders'=>'Providers','Backend / Providers / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nouveau','Backend / Providers / LabelAddress'=>'Adresse','Backend / Providers / LabelCookie URL'=>'URL cookie','Backend / Providers / LabelDescription'=>'Description','Backend / Providers / Label<translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">IAB Vendor ID</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">ID vendor IAB</translation-key>','Backend / Providers / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Providers / LabelName'=>'Nom','Backend / Providers / LabelOpt-out URL'=>'URL opt out','Backend / Providers / LabelPartners'=>'Partenaires','Backend / Providers / Label<translation-key id="Privacy-Url">Privacy URL</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Privacy-Url">URL confidentialité</translation-key>','Backend / Providers / HeadlineProvider Information'=>'Informations provider','Backend / Providers / LabelYou can optionally provide the <translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">IAB Vendor ID</translation-key> to add information about an IAB Vendor that is not part of the IAB TCF standard.'=>'Vous pouvez éventuellement indiquer l\'<translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">ID vendor IAB</translation-key> pour ajouter des informations sur un vendor IAB qui ne fait pas partie de la norme IAB TCF.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> section?'=>'Quelle est la finalité de la section <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> ?','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextFor legal compliance, every <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> must be linked to a specific <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'Pour des raisons de conformité légale, chaque <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> ou <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Bloqueur de contenu</translation-key> doit être lié à un <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> spécifique.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> is the company that delivers the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> (e.g., Google Analytics) or the content (e.g., YouTube videos).'=>'Le <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> est la société qui fournit le <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> (par ex., Google Analytics) ou le contenu (par ex., les vidéos YouTube).','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextVisitors should receive clear information about the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> responsible for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> or blocked content.'=>'Les providers doivent recevoir des informations claires sur le <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> responsable du <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> ou du contenu bloqué.','Backend / Providers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> configured.'=>'Aucun <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> n\'est configuré.','Backend / Providers / HeadlineProviders'=>'Providers','Backend / Providers / HeadlineReset Default Providers'=>'Réinitialiser les providers par défaut','Backend / Providers / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key>. They will be reset to their default settings. Your custom <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> and the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key> are not reset.'=>'Veuillez confirmer que vous souhaitez réinitialiser les <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key>. Ils seront réinitialisés à leurs paramètres par défaut. Vos <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> personnalisés et les <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> installés via la <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Bibliothèque</translation-key> ne sont pas réinitialisés.','Backend / Providers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Providers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Nom','Backend / Providers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Explication des symboles','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Owner-of-this-website">Owner of this website</translation-key>.'=>'Supprimer le <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>. Non disponible pour le <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> : <translation-key id="Owner-of-this-website">Propriétaire de ce site web</translation-key>.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'Modifier le <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Modifier : {{ name }}','Backend / Script Blockers / BreadcrumbScript Blockers'=>'Bloqueurs de script','Backend / Script Blockers / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nouveau','Backend / Script Blockers / Field LabelContent Blocker Global JavaScript'=>'Bloqueur de contenu Global JavaScript','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelHandles'=>'Handles','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelName'=>'Nom','Backend / Script Blockers / Label<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelPhrases'=>'Expressions','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelService Opt-in Script Tag'=>'Balise script service opt in','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelStatus'=>'Statut','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blocker Configuration'=>'Configuration bloqueur de script','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blocker Information'=>'Informations bloqueur de script','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blocker Settings'=>'Paramètres bloqueur de script','Backend / Script Blockers / HintIf your intention is to unblock previously blocked JavaScripts upon unblocking a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, please insert the provided JavaScript into the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field within your <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> settings.'=>'Si votre intention est de débloquer des JavaScripts précédemment bloqués lorsque vous débloquez un <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Bloqueur de contenu</translation-key>, veuillez insérer le JavaScript fourni dans le champ <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> dans les paramètres de votre <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Bloqueur de contenu</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> doit être défini. L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> doit être composé d\'au moins 3 caractères et ne peut contenir que : <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Script Blockers / HintThe name of the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Le nom du <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Bloqueur de script</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / HintTo allow the unblocking of previously blocked JavaScripts through user consent for a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, please insert the ensuing script tag into the field labeled <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> within your <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Pour permettre le déblocage de JavaScripts précédemment bloqués par le biais du consentement de l\'utilisateur d\'un <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, veuillez insérer la balise script suivante dans le champ intitulé <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Code opt in</translation-key> au sein de votre <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>. If the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is disabled, it will not block JavaScript.'=>'Statut de ce <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Bloqueur de script</translation-key>. Si le <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Bloqueur de script</translation-key> est désactivé, il ne bloquera pas JavaScript.','Backend / Script Blockers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> configured.'=>'Aucun <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Bloqueur de script</translation-key> n\'est configuré.','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blockers'=>'Bloqueurs de script','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Nom','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="On-Exist">OnExist</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="On-Exist">OnExist</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Phrases">Expressions</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Statut','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key> section?'=>'Quelle est la finalité de la section <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Bloqueurs de script</translation-key> ?','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Explication des symboles','Backend / Script Blockers / Tip / HeadlineLanguage independent'=>'Indépendant de la langue','Backend / Script Blockers / Tip / Text<translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key> are configured independently for all languages.'=>'Les <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Bloqueurs de script</translation-key> sont configurés indépendamment pour toutes les langues.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key> section allows you to block JavaScripts from <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> whose JavaScript you can\'t enter into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'La section <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Bloqueurs de script</translation-key> vous permet de bloquer les JavaScripts des <translation-key id="Plugins">Plug-ins</translation-key> dont le JavaScript ne peut être saisi dans le champ <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Code opt in</translation-key> d\'un <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextOnce a <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is created, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> provides an unblock JavaScript that can be entered into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. The JavaScript becomes unblocked once a visitor consents to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Une fois qu\'un <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Bloqueur de script</translation-key> est créé, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> fournit un JavaScript de déblocage qui peut être saisi dans le champ <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Code opt in</translation-key> d\'un <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Le JavaScript est débloqué dès qu\'un visiteur donne son consentement au <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextThis usually allows you to continue using your favorite plugins, but their JavaScript will only run when a visitor gave consent.'=>'Cela vous permet généralement de continuer à utiliser vos plug-ins préférés, mais leur JavaScript ne s\'exécutera que lorsqu\'un visiteur a donné son consentement.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is enabled and actively prevents JavaScript execution if the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key> matches a term configured in the system.'=>'Le <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Bloqueur de script</translation-key> est activé et empêche activement l\'exécution de JavaScript si les <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> ou les <translation-key id="Phrases">Expressions</translation-key> correspondent à un terme configuré dans le système.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>. Not available for a <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key>.'=>'Supprimer le <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Bloqueur de script</translation-key>. Non disponible pour un <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Bloqueur de script</translation-key> installé via la <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Bibliothèque</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Modifier le <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Bloqueur de script</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is inactive, allowing all JavaScript to execute without filtering or restricting based on <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>.'=>'Le <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Bloqueur de script</translation-key> est inactivé, ce qui permet l\'exécution de tout le JavaScript sans filtrage ni restriction sur la base de <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> ou d\'<translation-key id="Phrases">Expressions</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Cookie / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> configured.'=>'Aucun <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> n\'est configuré.','Backend / Service Cookie / ButtonAdd Cookie'=>'Ajouter un cookie','Backend / Service Cookie / FieldLifetime'=>'Durée de vie','Backend / Service Cookie / FieldName'=>'Nom','Backend / Service Cookie / HeadlineCookies'=>'Cookies','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineDescription'=>'Description','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineHostname'=>'Nom d\'hôte','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineLifetime'=>'Durée de vie','Backend / Service Cookie / Table Headline<translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Name">Nom</translation-key>','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlinePath'=>'Chemin d\'accès','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlinePurpose'=>'Finalité','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineType'=>'Type','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineYou may input all cookies utilized by the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> here. Typically, information regarding which cookies are used and their respective purposes can be found on the website of the service you intend to add. For instance, details about the cookies used by Google Analytics can be located in its knowledge base.'=>'Vous pouvez saisir ici tous les cookies utilisés par le <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Généralement, les informations concernant les cookies utilisés et leurs finalités respectives peuvent être trouvées sur le site web du service que vous avez l\'intention d\'ajouter. Par exemple, des détails sur les cookies utilisés par Google Analytics peuvent être trouvés dans sa base de connaissances.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section?'=>'Quelle est la finalité de la section <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> ?','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineInput fields explained'=>'Explication des champs de saisie','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Description">Description</translation-key>: Enter a description of the cookie and explain its purpose. This is optional, but recommended.'=>'<translation-key id="Description">Description</translation-key> : saisir une description du cookie et expliquer sa finalité. Cette information est facultative, mais recommandée.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineThe <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser\'s developer tools can be used to find the values for the <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key>, and <translation-key id="Lifetime">Lifetime</translation-key> fields.'=>'La section <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> des outils de développement de votre navigateur peut être utilisée pour trouver les valeurs des champs <translation-key id="Name">Nom</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Hostname">Nom d\'hôte</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Path">Chemin d\'accès</translation-key> et <translation-key id="Lifetime">Durée de vie</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Lifetime">Lifetime</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Expires">Expires</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser. Inform your visitor how many days the cookie will be stored or enter <translation-key id="Session">Session</translation-key> if the cookie is a session cookie and will be deleted when the browser is closed.'=>'<translation-key id="Lifetime">Durée de vie</translation-key> : ce champ correspond généralement à la colonne <translation-key id="Expires">Expire</translation-key> de la section <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> de votre navigateur. Indiquez à votre visiteur le nombre de jours pendant lesquels le cookie sera stocké ou entrez <translation-key id="Session">Session</translation-key> s\'il s\'agit d\'un cookie de session qui sera supprimé à la fermeture du navigateur.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineIf you find a date in the <translation-key id="Expires">Expires</translation-key> column, this means that the cookie is a persistent cookie and will be deleted on the specified date.'=>'Si vous trouvez une date dans la colonne <translation-key id="Expires">Expire</translation-key>, cela signifie que le cookie est un cookie persistant et qu\'il sera supprimé à la date spécifiée.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineIf you find the value <translation-key id="Session">Session</translation-key> in the <translation-key id="Expires">Expires</translation-key> column of your browser, this means that the cookie is a session cookie and will be deleted when you close your browser.'=>'Si vous trouvez la valeur <translation-key id="Session">Session</translation-key> dans la colonne <translation-key id="Expires">Expire</translation-key> de votre navigateur, cela signifie que le cookie est un cookie de session et qu\'il sera supprimé lorsque vous fermerez votre navigateur.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Domain">Domain</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser. You can enter <strong>#</strong> into this field and <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> will display the domain of your website in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Hostname">Nom d\'hôte</translation-key> : ce champ correspond généralement à la colonne <translation-key id="Domain">Domaine</translation-key> de la section <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> de votre navigateur. Vous pouvez saisir <strong>#</strong> dans ce champ et <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> affichera le domaine de votre site web dans la <translation-key id="Dialog">Boîte de dialogue</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser.'=>'<translation-key id="Name">Nom</translation-key> : le champ correspond généralement à la colonne <translation-key id="Name">Nom</translation-key> dans la section <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> de votre navigateur.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser. Usually, the path is <strong>/</strong>.'=>'<translation-key id="Path">Chemin d\'accès</translation-key> : ce champ correspond généralement à la colonne <translation-key id="Path">Chemin d\'accès</translation-key> de la section <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> de votre navigateur. Le chemin d\'accès est généralement <strong>/</strong>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Purpose">Purpose</translation-key>: We distinguish in two types of <translation-key id="Purposes">Purposes</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Functional">Functional</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Tracking">Tracking</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Purpose">Finalité</translation-key> : nous distinguons deux types de <translation-key id="Purposes">Finalités</translation-key> : <translation-key id="Functional">Fonctionnels</translation-key> et <translation-key id="Tracking">Suivi</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Functional">Functional</translation-key> cookies are required for the basic functionality of the website.'=>'Les cookies <translation-key id="Functional">Fonctionnels</translation-key> sont nécessaires à la fonctionnalité de base du site web.','Backend / Country / CountryNorway'=>'Norvège','Backend / Library / Button TitleRefresh Library'=>'Actualiser la bibliothèque','Backend / Country / CountryNepal'=>'Népal','Backend / Li